response.original_title: Chikara: Aniversario 3 - Dodging the Sophomore Jinx
response.overview: History is made, as Blind Rage retires from fulltime competition, and Mister ZERO and Shane Storm form Men@Work for the very first time! Everyone, including Cavalier Jones, has something on the line in the "Ultimate Jeopardy" trios match that ends the feud between Mike Quackenbush and F.I.S.T., and The Toxic Trio!
response.title: Chikara: Aniversario 3 - Dodging the Sophomore Jinx
